$interpreted: Minnie: The purple one lets the light through and the other one is uniquely tailored. Which one do you like?
Sophie: I think whatever Mom picks will look great~
Ordinary Person: I can't believe that sideshow that calls itself a circus can be mocked so hard and still have the gall to keep performing.
Well-know Local: Right!? Hide under a rock, why don't you~
Sophie: What happened to Morgan's Marvelous Circus!?
Minnie: Soph...my chest is hurting. Let's go back home and rest.
Sophie: Mom, you don't have to keep pretending...
Minnie: I'm really not feeling good...
Sophie: Actually...I've always known you were faking it.
Minnie: How'd you know!?
Sophie: From the moment you "fainted" I knew...
Sophie: I mean, I have been acting ever since I was a child. I can tell if someone is putting on a performance.
Minnie: Little Soph, I, I...
Sophie: I know you just want keep me close, so you made up a bunch of lies.
Sophie: I know it's only because they wanted what's best for me that Hanbei and them left me here.
Minnie: Well then, just stay here and keep your mother company.
Sophie: I am happy to be living with you...but when I heard what happened to them...
Sophie: I realized that the circus is the most important family I've had. I've decided that I still want to live with them.
Minnie: No! I won't allow it! I'm your mother, and that makes me your real family!
Minnie: No matter what they've done, they'll always be outsiders!
Sophie: Sorry, Mom. But I must go.
Minnie: My Soph, don't go! Don't leave me...
Ru-yi: I miss you so much~~
Rune: Me...too.
Hanbei: Cheer up. Otherwise, Sophie's gonna get even more upset.
Hutchinson: He's right. We've got to keep performing like everything is normal. If not, there is no way Sophie is going to be comfortable staying with Minnie.
Hanbei: Okay! Everyone ready to hit the stage?
Hanbei: Bringing smiles to everyone! We are Morgan's Marvelous Circus!
Hanbei: Let's welcome the whaliest of whales, Ru-yi! Then there's the victor of victors, the hot hot-shot, Rune!
Bitter Bert: We don't want to see that buff doof perform. Let's see that smokeshow do a thing or two!
Hanbei: ...*cough*!
Hanbei: Next, let's welcome the legendary Deer demihuman with giant antlers——Hutchinson!!
Hutchinson: Ay-ya!!
Ru-yi: Hutchinson! Are you okay?
Bitter Bert: Wow. Who falls on such a dinky rope slide?
Hanbei: What did you say!?
Hutchinson: Everybody relax. No need to get upset. If a fight breaks out, Sophie is going to get upset.
Ru-yi: Yeah. Sophie always said we've got to bring a smile to everybody, not go around hurtin' folks.
Sophie: She's right. It's our job to make the people smile.
Rune: Sophie!
Sophie: It's also our duty to teach those rude audience members a lesson~
Sophie: Morgan's Marvelous Circus, let's go!
Ru-yi: Sophie! You came back~
Sophie: This is my home. If I didn't come back then where would I go?
Hanbei: Hmph. Look who's back. Without you, we were doing just fine.
Hutchinson: Hanbei, is that what you really think?
Hanbei: Hey airhead, didn't you say you didn't like this rambling lifestyle? Why wouldn't you stay with Minnie and avoid the suffering?
Sophie: Although I was happy with my mom…
Sophie: ever since we split, I know what it means to not have somebody to rely on.
Sophie: I realized that I've always had a family, and that the most important people in my life are all of you.
Hanbei: Airhead, a little late don't you think...?
Minnie: Soph, without you by my side, I don't know how I am going to live alone...
Sophie: Even though I will live here with the circus, I promise to come visit you when I'm free. You're welcome to come see our shows!
Minnie: Really? I can come watch your show?
Sophie: Of course! I'll never be able to replace my mom.
Sophie: We all welcome you. Isn't that right, Hanbei?
Hanbei: *cough*...as long as you don't try to take Sophie away or lie to us about everything, then you're welcome.
Minnie: Soph...thank you, all of you...
Hanbei: Airhead, I still think it took a little too long~
Hutchinson: Hanbei, you must be patient with women~
Ru-yi: Sophie~ are you ready yet?
Sophie: Coming, comingg~
Sophie: What do you think?
Ru-yi: Whaaa! Amazing!
Hutchinson: Sophie, recommending that your mother open a clothing shop was a great idea. It really suits her and gives her something to live for.
Hanbei: Hmph. Looks like when Minnie isn't faking being sick, she's got a pretty good eye.
Sophie: Well, next time we perform I'll make sure to wear this outfit ~~
